name: 6 Queens - Queen Nandi
description:
A fierce warrior Mother.
A blood line pure and thoroughbred.
She calms with her breath.
She soothes with her touch.
She wields only a sword at those that approach with no prior invitation.
She protects her children with a nourished bosom.
A golden hand that can yield from any crop.
A Divine Giver of pure love hope and grace.
